Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起把白祭辦起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就我們5個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走一步是一步了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚結果會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們一定要放聲高歌
